title: Unreal Tournament GOLD Edition (English/Spanish)
description:
Unreal Tournament Gold Edition
==============================

It is a multilingual edition with the following features:

-High Definition Textures CD 2 integrated S3 textures patch to avoid crashing.

-Patch 436 "NO CD" already applied.

-Including the 4 official mods.

-Including new renderers OpenGL and DirectX 10, Windows 7 x64 prepared and tested in 32bit, works with 2 and 4 cores, smooth speed variation.

-Included new sound drivers, OpenAL (Required oalinst.exe install directory "system" of UT) and Fmod.

-Retired Drivers older, obsolete files and links to websites of online games.

-Added function to change wallpaper and updated online server browser.



Enjoy it, do not let this game die, (Although there are still 700 servers online!) ...
